import React, { useRef } from 'react'
import { useGLTF, useAnimations } from '@react-three/drei'

export default function Scene(props) {
  const group = useRef()
  const { nodes, materials, animations } = useGLTF('/model.glb')
  const { actions } = useAnimations(animations, group)
  return (
    <group ref={group} {...props} dispose={null} position={[0, -1, 0]}>
      <group name="Scene">
        <group name="Door_Group001" position={[-4.95, -0.47, -4.95]} scale={0.48}>
          <mesh name="DoorFrame004" geometry={nodes.DoorFrame004.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']}>
            <mesh name="Door004" geometry={nodes.Door004.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']} position={[0.42, 1.05, 0.02]}>
              <mesh name="Handle_Back004" geometry={nodes.Handle_Back004.geometry} material={materials['Gray white plastic']} position={[-0.76, 0, -0.01]} />
              <mesh name="Handle_Front004" geometry={nodes.Handle_Front004.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']} position={[-0.76, 0, -0.03]} rotation={[-Math.PI, 0, 0]} />
            </mesh>
          </mesh>
        </group>
        <group name="Window_Group001" position={[-3.82, 0.09, -5.97]} rotation={[0, -1.57, 0]} scale={0.39}>
          <mesh name="WindowFrame001" geometry={nodes.WindowFrame001.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']}>
            <group name="WindowL001" position={[-0.59, 0.03, 0.02]}>
              <mesh name="WindowL001_1" geometry={nodes.WindowL001_1.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']} />
              <mesh name="WindowL001_2" geometry={nodes.WindowL001_2.geometry} material={materials['Material.008']} />
              <mesh name="Handle002" geometry={nodes.Handle002.geometry} material={materials['Plastic_Handle_material.001']} position={[0.04, 0.48, 0.04]} />
            </group>
            <group name="WindowR001" position={[0.59, 0.03, 0.06]}>
              <mesh name="WindowR001_1" geometry={nodes.WindowR001_1.geometry} material={materials['Material.009']} />
              <mesh name="WindowR001_2" geometry={nodes.WindowR001_2.geometry} material={materials['Material.008']} />
              <mesh name="Handle003" geometry={nodes.Handle003.geometry} material={materials['Plastic_Handle_material.001']} position={[-0.03, 0.48, 0.04]} />
            </group>
            <mesh name="Windows_Sill001" geometry={nodes.Windows_Sill001.geometry} material={materials['Sill_material.001']} position={[0, 0, 0.1]} />
          </mesh>
        </group>
        <group name="Cube003" position={[-4.9, 0.52, -5.97]}>
          <mesh name="Cube004" geometry={nodes.Cube004.geometry} material={materials['Wood Parquet']} />
          <mesh name="Cube004_1" geometry={nodes.Cube004_1.geometry} material={materials['Material.003']} />
        </group>
      </group>
    </group>
  )
}

useGLTF.preload('/model.glb')
